WEBVTT

00:03.006 --> 00:11.240
Imagination is something that is made up and that you create in your mind.

00:11.469 --> 00:13.328
You're creative.

00:13.426 --> 00:16.781
You think of stuff that nobody else thinks of.

00:17.067 --> 00:29.649
You get to talk and pretend you're something like a ballerina or a rock star or a fairy.

00:30.752 --> 00:34.225
It means you think of being sadder in your head.

00:34.937 --> 00:36.545
It's like daydreaming but...

00:38.241 --> 00:39.646
Kind of like dreaming.

00:39.841 --> 00:41.131
...but you do it...

00:41.922 --> 00:44.844
Yeah, something like what he said.

